{"tid":137613,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Linux 喺幾日前終於fix好咗一個有11年歷史嘅安全漏洞","createTime":"2017-02-28T03:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T11:31:14.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8cd69552305b81516555b0c33779655fb5e79e3","tid":137613,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Linux專案修補可能存在11年之久的最高存取權限漏洞<br />\n<a href=\"http://times.hinet.net/mobile/news/20045991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimes.hinet.net%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2F20045991&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8fe0edd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://times.hinet.net/mobile/news/20045991</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\nLinux核心開發人員在上周修補了一個<span style=\"color: red;\">藏匿了11年的本地端權限擴張漏洞，可能讓駭客取得系統的最高權限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span><br />\n<br />\n該漏洞是由Google的實習生Andrey Konovalov利用Google所建立的安全稽核工具syzkaller找到的，現身於Linux核心中的數據壅塞控制協議（Datagram Congestion Control Protocol，DCCP）中，而且可能早在Linux於2005年開始支援DCCP時就有了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n此一編號為CVE-2017-6074的安全漏洞屬於記憶體重複釋放（double-free）漏洞，將允許本地端無特權的使用者修改Linux核心的記憶體，以執行阻斷服務攻擊或是取得最高權限。<br />\n<br />\n目前已確定的最早受到波及的Linux核心版本是2006年9月釋出的2.6.18，但Konovalov認為該漏洞很可能在Linux核心第一次支援DCCP時的2.5.14就存在了，而那是在2005年10月，迄今已超過11年，且很多現在的Linux版本的預設值都啟用了會受到影響的CONFIG_IP_DCCP。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員警告，儘管它不是一個遠端攻擊漏洞，但這類的本地端權限擴張漏洞也不容小覷，若結合了其他允許遠端駭客取得低權限的漏洞就可能帶來重大風險。<br />\n<br />\n包括紅帽、Debian、Ubuntu與SUSE皆已修補了該漏洞。"},{"pid":"7218725e82b7270d6b1c2738167ab774c30c471c","tid":137613,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"次次update完先見到舊版有漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9c5741a0a7ea0a81cc3a02b59690ac958b9ec4","tid":137613,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"之後好似有個 bug 係 == 寫左做 = 又係10幾年"},{"pid":"0eb9df279a3fd79a7746d0eaf61617e6bd5dda56","tid":137613,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前好似有個 bug 係 == 寫左做 = 又係10幾年</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f4c89641a0aa7e7e07aa367c2b59e35ac895c987","tid":137613,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前好似有個 bug 係 == 寫左做 = 又係10幾年</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾得意<br />\ncow好似都有5,6 年"}]}